data.description: Immerse yourself in luxury living in this captivating 6-bedroom oasis in Otay Ranch! Step inside and be greeted by a breathtaking open concept granite kitchen. Imagine whipping up culinary delights with gleaming stainless steel appliances, a center island for food prep and entertaining, and decorative pendant lights that add a touch of sparkle. Deep, rich, upgraded engineered hardwood floors flowing seamlessly throughout the main living areas. These floors create a warm and inviting atmosphere that's easy to maintain. A formal living room fit for grand occasions. French doors open onto the patio, blurring the lines between indoor and outdoor living, while built-in shelving and elegant plantation shutters add a touch of sophistication all throughout the home. With the low-maintenance yard, spend less time on yard work and more time enjoying the California sunshine in your private outdoor oasis, perfect for hosting memorable gatherings with friends and family. Home is equipped with paid solar panels. All of this in addition to a welcoming neighborhood with amenities such as Montecito club house and pool, parks, trails, shopping centers and award winning schools.
